text: Connor Metcalfe (born 5 November 1999) is an Australian soccer player. He plays for FC St. Pauli in the Bundesliga and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:People from Newcastle, New South Wales Category:Sportspeople from New South Wales
